1
00:00:17,940 --> 00:00:21,260
♪The falling snow♪

2
00:00:21,620 --> 00:00:25,180
♪Is bitter cold♪

3
00:00:27,300 --> 00:00:29,980
♪My sigh♪

4
00:00:30,420 --> 00:00:34,460
♪Misted the path in front of me♪

5
00:00:36,620 --> 00:00:42,740
♪The moonlight knows my intention♪

6
00:00:44,860 --> 00:00:51,300
♪I just want to make a place
for me in your heart♪

7
00:00:53,820 --> 00:00:57,620
♪I laugh and I cry♪

8
00:00:58,340 --> 00:01:02,100
♪Quietly building a pond in my heart♪

9
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:06,780
♪I accept all the gifts from sorrow♪

10
00:01:07,580 --> 00:01:11,420
♪I can't let down my regrets♪

11
00:01:12,060 --> 00:01:15,860
♪I won't admit defeat♪

12
00:01:16,460 --> 00:01:20,260
♪I slowly chew
on the bitterness of life♪

13
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:24,540
♪The fragrance remains the same
after the bleak winter♪

14
00:01:25,340 --> 00:01:29,540
♪Awaiting spring to color
the way back home♪

15
00:01:31,020 --> 00:01:36,340
[The Double]

16
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:39,060
[Episode 7]

17
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:42,640
A young official
in a clean white robe indeed.

18
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,040
I don't like the way

19
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,840
you talk so formally to me.

20
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,350
It makes me uncomfortable.

21
00:01:51,070 --> 00:01:51,680
Kneel.

22
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:52,920
Your Highness.

23
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,590
Kneel.

24
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:07,280
Astounding.

25
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,750
Even the way you kneel

26
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:11,840
looks better than other men.

27
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,280
I am glad that you like it.

28
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:17,120
I dislike righteous officials

29
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,910
and those in clean white robes.

30
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,840
I love the way you look at me

31
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:25,430
with all the frustration kept inside.

32
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,080
Shen.

33
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:29,750
Play along, won't you?

34
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,710
Your plan is an unprecedented one.

35
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,750
This is a national affair.

36
00:02:34,310 --> 00:02:35,400
I can't obey the order.

37
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,680
That's very persistent of you.

38
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:40,430
Very well.

39
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,120
Rise and eat.

40
00:02:47,340 --> 00:02:49,800
[Govern the people, serve Heaven]

41
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,520
The Entry Exam
is on the 10th next month.

42
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:53,030
As for the guidelines and rules,

43
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,800
they are in the memorial.

44
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,840
It's a relief to leave the Entry Exam

45
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,710
in your hands.

46
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:13,120
Your Majesty, the Eldest Princess
wishes to see you.

47
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,750
Your Majesty.

48
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:28,190
Scholar Shen is here too.

49
00:03:29,150 --> 00:03:30,840
Am I interrupting your conversation?

50
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:32,190
Not at all.

51
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,120
That concludes my report.

52
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:36,310
I should go now.

53
00:03:38,580 --> 00:03:40,080
[Govern the people, serve Heaven]

54
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,030
Scholar Shen.

55
00:03:42,190 --> 00:03:43,560
I came with an idea.

56
00:03:43,910 --> 00:03:45,400
I'd like your opinion on the idea.

57
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,520
The Entry Exam is
just around the corner.

58
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:56,360
It was always the same questions.

59
00:03:56,630 --> 00:03:58,520
We never got any remarkable talents.

60
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:02,310
I have a better idea
for the exam this year.

61
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,680
What might it be?

62
00:04:04,310 --> 00:04:07,030
Why not let the men
and women compete in teams?

63
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:09,000
Nonsense.

64
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:12,280
The Imperial Academy and
the School of Integrity are not the same.

65
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:14,400
Men and women can sit for the same exam.

66
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:17,560
Do you assume the noblewomen

67
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:20,120
would be a liability
for the noblemen of the capital?

68
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,390
That's not it.

69
00:04:22,390 --> 00:04:23,070
Your Majesty.

70
00:04:24,310 --> 00:04:25,510
Do not forget,

71
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:29,390
I was sent away as a hostage
to bring peace to the Great Yan.

72
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:33,560
You are sitting on that throne,

73
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:35,800
thanks to me.

74
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:43,120
Do not underestimate
the women of this nation.

75
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:45,120
When time calls for it,

76
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,120
we can be as capable as men.

77
00:04:49,070 --> 00:04:50,630
It's high time you gave them a chance

78
00:04:50,630 --> 00:04:52,430
to sit the same exam as the men.

79
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:58,390
What do you think of this idea,
Scholar Shen?

80
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:10,720
Very well.

81
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:13,240
We proceed with your idea.

82
00:05:15,060 --> 00:05:16,180
Many thanks, Your Majesty.

83
00:05:23,620 --> 00:05:27,540
[Govern the people, serve Heaven]

84
00:05:37,020 --> 00:05:37,770
Shen.

85
00:05:38,770 --> 00:05:40,740
I came here because of you.

86
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:44,450
Do not be wayward again.

87
00:05:45,380 --> 00:05:46,890
Lest you want me to show you

88
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:48,770
how to be obedient.

89
00:06:12,420 --> 00:06:17,260
[Taiji Hall]

90
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:31,300
[Jiang's Residence]

91
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:32,300
A light stroke.

92
00:06:32,550 --> 00:06:33,150
Like so?

93
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:37,670
Not bad.

94
00:06:39,550 --> 00:06:40,180
Jiang Li!

95
00:06:41,110 --> 00:06:41,710
Jiang Li!

96
00:06:42,710 --> 00:06:44,350
I have an interesting story for you.

97
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:46,060
What do you mean?

98
00:06:46,940 --> 00:06:49,620
The Imperial Academy
and the School of Integrity will have

99
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:51,380
men and women
sitting for the exam together.

100
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:53,030
That has never been done before.

101
00:06:54,470 --> 00:06:56,420
Why the unique method this year?

102
00:06:56,670 --> 00:06:57,470
You know nothing.

103
00:06:57,740 --> 00:06:58,940
The new Entry Exam

104
00:06:59,110 --> 00:07:00,350
was approved by His Majesty.

105
00:07:00,910 --> 00:07:02,670
Scholar Shen Yurong
of the Selection Exam

106
00:07:02,670 --> 00:07:03,620
is seeing to the matter.

107
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:04,990
From what I heard,

108
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:06,790
His Majesty will personally meet

109
00:07:06,790 --> 00:07:08,790
whoever has the best score.

110
00:07:10,910 --> 00:07:12,500
This is a chance of a lifetime.

111
00:07:12,790 --> 00:07:14,710
Where do I find a lady to team up?

112
00:07:15,030 --> 00:07:15,550
Me.

113
00:07:19,110 --> 00:07:20,110
You?

114
00:07:30,550 --> 00:07:30,990
Ouch...

115
00:07:31,820 --> 00:07:32,350
Ouch...

116
00:07:33,420 --> 00:07:34,260
Jiang Li.

117
00:07:34,860 --> 00:07:37,350
You're not even a member
of the School of Integrity.

118
00:07:37,590 --> 00:07:38,470
However,

119
00:07:38,470 --> 00:07:40,860
I must talk you out
of this bizarre idea.

120
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:42,380
The School of Integrity

121
00:07:42,740 --> 00:07:43,860
is for the daughters

122
00:07:44,180 --> 00:07:47,820
of beauty and talents from
families of officials in the capital.

123
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:49,180
You look

124
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:50,230
somewhat passable.

125
00:07:50,300 --> 00:07:51,260
But that look

126
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:52,710
is unique to you.

127
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:54,060
As for your talent...

128
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:56,940
You have a long way to go!

129
00:07:58,180 --> 00:08:00,060
Even if my uncle
pull some strings for you

130
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:01,740
and got you into
the School of Integrity,

131
00:08:02,110 --> 00:08:03,990
you'll still get eliminated.

132
00:08:04,470 --> 00:08:07,860
You'll be the greatest
laughingstock of the city.

133
00:08:10,790 --> 00:08:11,940
It's worth it

134
00:08:12,350 --> 00:08:13,470
to give the people a good laugh.

135
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:15,350
You're just asking for trouble.

136
00:08:15,790 --> 00:08:17,550
My uncle will never let you participate.

137
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:18,500
Let's have a bet.

138
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:19,940
If you get in,

139
00:08:20,470 --> 00:08:22,710
Little Backbone and I

140
00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:25,230
will walk a lap upside-down
at the Imperial Academy.

141
00:08:25,620 --> 00:08:26,230
One whole lap.

142
00:08:32,380 --> 00:08:33,540
Can you even walk upside-down?

143
00:08:34,230 --> 00:08:36,710
Show us now if you can.

144
00:08:39,070 --> 00:08:39,660
Why you...

145
00:08:40,350 --> 00:08:41,020
You two...

146
00:08:42,260 --> 00:08:43,430
I'm done wasting my time on you.

147
00:08:54,950 --> 00:08:57,780
I haven't seen Bing Ji in a few days.

148
00:08:58,190 --> 00:08:59,540
According to Mrs. Shen,

149
00:08:59,660 --> 00:09:01,660
Bing Ji has caught a cold lately.

150
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:03,500
She will visit you

151
00:09:03,900 --> 00:09:05,020
when he gets well.

152
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:10,830
Using a child for a show of displeasure?

153
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:14,890
Madam Jiang,

154
00:09:15,020 --> 00:09:16,220
The Second Lady wants to see you.

155
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:18,020
Let her in.

156
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:27,620
Grandmother.

157
00:09:28,050 --> 00:09:28,890
Li.

158
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:30,740
Why the sudden visit?

159
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:32,690
I came to thank you.

160
00:09:33,620 --> 00:09:35,220
Bai Xue is kind and thoughtful.

161
00:09:35,690 --> 00:09:36,860
She is very capable

162
00:09:37,260 --> 00:09:38,290
and a rare talent.

163
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:40,530
She is your servant now.

164
00:09:41,140 --> 00:09:42,930
Handle her with care.

165
00:09:43,530 --> 00:09:44,220
Grandmother.

166
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:47,460
I have a request.

167
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:50,050
Sit.

168
00:09:54,170 --> 00:09:56,100
Tell me what this is about.

169
00:09:56,650 --> 00:09:58,810
I've been in the Zhennv Hall
for ten years.

170
00:09:59,460 --> 00:10:01,100
My reputation was tarnished.

171
00:10:01,690 --> 00:10:03,570
Father brought me back.

172
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:06,140
The Jiang family restored my reputation.

173
00:10:06,930 --> 00:10:08,460
But to the others,

174
00:10:08,810 --> 00:10:10,930
I am always the same sinner.

175
00:10:13,140 --> 00:10:14,140
Li.

176
00:10:15,140 --> 00:10:16,740
You overthink too much.

177
00:10:17,460 --> 00:10:18,170
Grandmother.

178
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:21,460
I want to study
at the School of Integrity.

179
00:10:21,930 --> 00:10:23,260
I want to hone my character

180
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:26,810
and make a name for myself.

181
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:29,340
It's great for a woman
to pursue knowledge.

182
00:10:29,770 --> 00:10:30,890
Do you think so too?

183
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:32,020
Certainly.

184
00:10:32,650 --> 00:10:34,500
The world should know

185
00:10:34,690 --> 00:10:37,170
how capable you are.

186
00:10:39,620 --> 00:10:40,290
Grandmother.

187
00:10:41,170 --> 00:10:41,810
Look.

188
00:10:43,170 --> 00:10:44,740
I wrote this.

189
00:10:49,260 --> 00:10:50,500
Good handwriting.

190
00:10:51,060 --> 00:10:52,180
[Wang Jiuling, despite not living to
100 like Peng Zu, guided the Fan Zhong.]

191
00:10:53,290 --> 00:10:55,860
The Zhennv Hall is not a place to learn.

192
00:10:56,410 --> 00:10:57,980
You must have practiced hard.

193
00:10:58,740 --> 00:11:00,140
Knowing you appreciate it,

194
00:11:00,460 --> 00:11:01,890
it was worth the effort.

195
00:11:02,980 --> 00:11:03,570
Come.

196
00:11:06,890 --> 00:11:09,380
Your father had
excellent handwriting as well.

197
00:11:10,410 --> 00:11:12,890
After becoming the Prime Minister,

198
00:11:13,260 --> 00:11:14,810
a few words he wrote

199
00:11:15,290 --> 00:11:18,170
became the treasured
calligraphy artwork.

200
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:20,650
So, he stopped writing.

201
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:26,770
Show these writings to him.

202
00:11:27,100 --> 00:11:28,290
He will be thrilled.

203
00:11:29,170 --> 00:11:31,980
Then, ask him to send you to the school.

204
00:11:32,170 --> 00:11:35,530
I'll prepare
the necessary stationery for you.

205
00:11:38,890 --> 00:11:40,050
I wouldn't want to trouble you.

206
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:47,810
Are you concerned
this might displease someone?

207
00:11:49,770 --> 00:11:51,020
Do not be concerned.

208
00:11:51,570 --> 00:11:53,620
I'm keeping this paper.

209
00:11:54,380 --> 00:11:57,810
I'll convince your father.

210
00:11:58,530 --> 00:11:59,620
Thank you.

211
00:12:00,620 --> 00:12:02,340
Have some pear soup.

212
00:12:03,460 --> 00:12:04,050
Sure.

213
00:12:06,410 --> 00:12:08,220
These are Li's handwriting.

214
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:09,650
What do you think?

215
00:12:09,650 --> 00:12:10,050
[Wang Jiuling, despite not living to
100 like Peng Zu, guided the Fan Zhong.]

216
00:12:10,050 --> 00:12:11,930
Upright and with the right force.

217
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:15,170
Straight and not without a shine.

218
00:12:15,770 --> 00:12:17,410
Even you agree it's good handwriting.

219
00:12:17,980 --> 00:12:19,220
Is this enough to enroll her

220
00:12:19,460 --> 00:12:21,410
in the School of Integrity?

221
00:12:23,290 --> 00:12:26,570
Li wants to study
at the School of Integrity?

222
00:12:27,050 --> 00:12:28,170
What do you think?

223
00:12:32,380 --> 00:12:33,050
But...

224
00:12:33,460 --> 00:12:34,930
Li is passionate about learning.

225
00:12:35,340 --> 00:12:36,650
I'm glad that she does.

226
00:12:37,740 --> 00:12:41,050
But the School of Integrity
is unlike the average schools.

227
00:12:41,810 --> 00:12:43,140
Every year, women would get expelled

228
00:12:43,340 --> 00:12:45,740
due to lackluster results.

229
00:12:46,570 --> 00:12:49,290
Li barely had an education before this.

230
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:54,100
I'm worried the people there
might give her a hard time.

231
00:12:55,860 --> 00:12:57,890
Yuanbai is the current Chief Secretary.

232
00:12:58,410 --> 00:12:59,500
His children

233
00:12:59,690 --> 00:13:02,380
must not be illiterate
and mocked by the people.

234
00:13:02,810 --> 00:13:04,740
After years in the Zhennv Hall,

235
00:13:05,050 --> 00:13:07,020
Li still managed
to have remarkable handwriting.

236
00:13:07,340 --> 00:13:09,410
She has worked hard to accomplish this.

237
00:13:09,530 --> 00:13:11,100
Bullies won't dwindle her spirit.

238
00:13:11,690 --> 00:13:12,690
I think

239
00:13:13,290 --> 00:13:14,380
the handwriting

240
00:13:14,980 --> 00:13:16,980
is better than Ruoyao's,
who you practically raised.

241
00:13:24,810 --> 00:13:26,650
Indeed, Madam Jiang.

242
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:29,740
However, we don't get to decide

243
00:13:30,140 --> 00:13:31,570
if Li can get a place there.

244
00:13:32,100 --> 00:13:32,890
My husband,

245
00:13:33,380 --> 00:13:35,050
we should hire a tutor

246
00:13:35,170 --> 00:13:36,530
to test Li's standards.

247
00:13:37,020 --> 00:13:38,530
Knowing her capability

248
00:13:38,860 --> 00:13:41,100
is the best for her and this family.

249
00:13:42,980 --> 00:13:44,170
Makes sense.

250
00:13:44,290 --> 00:13:45,410
Ask Yuan Ping

251
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:48,980
to hire the tutor
who taught Jiang Jingrui.

252
00:13:49,620 --> 00:13:52,260
He is experienced and sharp.

253
00:13:52,530 --> 00:13:53,690
He once said

254
00:13:53,690 --> 00:13:56,380
that Jingrui would make it
into the Imperial Academy.

255
00:13:56,650 --> 00:13:57,740
He was right.

256
00:13:57,930 --> 00:13:58,460
Indeed.

257
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:00,810
I'll go to Yuan Ping later.

258
00:14:01,530 --> 00:14:02,530
Wait.

259
00:14:03,170 --> 00:14:05,980
The two schools are not the same.

260
00:14:07,650 --> 00:14:10,570
Well, who should we hire?

261
00:14:10,930 --> 00:14:12,380
I know someone for the task.

262
00:14:13,020 --> 00:14:14,620
If he thinks Jiang Li can make it past

263
00:14:14,930 --> 00:14:16,860
the selection
of the School of Integrity,

264
00:14:17,140 --> 00:14:19,220
the others will have to
accept the decision made by us

265
00:14:19,340 --> 00:14:20,460
and the school.

266
00:14:32,980 --> 00:14:33,930
Scholar Shen.

267
00:14:37,380 --> 00:14:37,980
Prime Minister Jiang.

268
00:14:38,050 --> 00:14:39,050
Let's have a word.

269
00:14:45,050 --> 00:14:47,860
You are in charge
of the Entry Exam for both institutes.

270
00:14:48,020 --> 00:14:50,020
That's a tremendous task.

271
00:14:50,570 --> 00:14:52,410
Do you have some time?

272
00:14:52,570 --> 00:14:53,740
Thank you for the concern.

273
00:14:54,020 --> 00:14:55,930
It's my day off. I have some time.

274
00:14:56,530 --> 00:14:57,380
Perfect.

275
00:14:57,740 --> 00:14:59,170
I need a favour from you.

276
00:15:00,100 --> 00:15:03,170
My daughter Jiang Li wants
to enroll in the School of Integrity.

277
00:15:03,380 --> 00:15:04,380
But as you know,

278
00:15:04,460 --> 00:15:06,620
she has never gone to a proper school.

279
00:15:07,100 --> 00:15:09,570
She is your daughter.
I believe she will do remarkably.

280
00:15:10,140 --> 00:15:11,460
I hope you are right.

281
00:15:12,690 --> 00:15:14,810
Test her standards for me.

282
00:15:15,170 --> 00:15:17,690
It should give my wife and I
an ease of the mind.

283
00:15:30,860 --> 00:15:33,890
Is there a problem, Scholar Shen?

284
00:15:35,860 --> 00:15:36,930
A request from an elder.

285
00:15:37,290 --> 00:15:38,810
I'll do my best.

286
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:40,860
Much appreciated.

287
00:15:58,050 --> 00:15:58,890
Mrs. Jiang.

288
00:15:59,170 --> 00:16:01,690
Scholar Shen, take a seat.

289
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:16,260
Have some tea.

290
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:18,290
I'll bring Li here.

291
00:16:23,620 --> 00:16:24,650
Scholar Shen.

292
00:16:25,380 --> 00:16:27,530
Li spent ten years at the Zhennv Hall.

293
00:16:27,860 --> 00:16:29,770
If she offends you in any way,

294
00:16:30,100 --> 00:16:31,460
I hope you won't mind.

295
00:16:32,260 --> 00:16:33,260
I won't.

296
00:16:36,690 --> 00:16:37,530
Scholar Shen.

297
00:16:42,620 --> 00:16:43,810
A token of appreciation.

298
00:16:52,140 --> 00:16:54,380
This gesture is unnecessary.

299
00:16:55,410 --> 00:16:57,380
I'll take it that you accept the silver.

300
00:16:57,770 --> 00:16:59,650
Remember to do your job well.

301
00:17:00,770 --> 00:17:02,860
Li is the firstborn.

302
00:17:03,100 --> 00:17:04,850
It shouldn't be a problem for her

303
00:17:04,850 --> 00:17:06,020
to get into the School of Integrity.

304
00:17:06,980 --> 00:17:10,050
Scholar Shen,
do not leave me disappointed.

305
00:17:21,420 --> 00:17:24,020
I thought the money was
meant for another purpose.

306
00:17:25,090 --> 00:17:27,370
Why are you helping Jiang Li?

307
00:17:27,740 --> 00:17:30,940
Do you know why I asked
Scholar Shen to test her?

308
00:17:31,420 --> 00:17:32,740
I have no idea.

309
00:17:33,090 --> 00:17:35,530
Scholar Shen came
from an impoverished family.

310
00:17:35,980 --> 00:17:37,290
When he became the Principal Graduate,

311
00:17:37,610 --> 00:17:39,770
he held a banquet
to meet the people in high places.

312
00:17:39,850 --> 00:17:41,180
But no one attended.

313
00:17:41,530 --> 00:17:42,850
It was all for nothing.

314
00:17:44,330 --> 00:17:46,940
Therefore, he hates

315
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:49,050
the privileged who look down on others.

316
00:17:49,610 --> 00:17:51,850
No money can sway him.

317
00:17:52,130 --> 00:17:53,260
I hired him

318
00:17:53,610 --> 00:17:55,770
so he could hate Jiang Li to the bones.

319
00:18:45,530 --> 00:18:46,940
Greetings,

320
00:18:50,370 --> 00:18:51,420
Scholar Shen.

321
00:19:09,570 --> 00:19:11,050
Where are your manners?

322
00:19:29,460 --> 00:19:31,020
You remind me...

323
00:19:34,330 --> 00:19:35,330
of someone close.

324
00:19:38,290 --> 00:19:41,330
I apologise for the behaviour.

325
00:19:44,290 --> 00:19:47,130
My father often talks about you.

326
00:19:48,500 --> 00:19:49,980
It's an honor

327
00:19:50,980 --> 00:19:53,570
to have your guidance.

328
00:19:53,700 --> 00:19:54,770
When the incense burns out,

329
00:19:55,370 --> 00:19:58,220
I'll mark the paper.

330
00:20:09,290 --> 00:20:11,090
Have you been to Qingcheng Mountain?

331
00:20:19,700 --> 00:20:20,570
Yes.

332
00:20:28,370 --> 00:20:30,020
With whom?

333
00:20:33,370 --> 00:20:34,740
She is gone.

334
00:20:36,090 --> 00:20:37,370
Let's not talk about her.

335
00:20:45,090 --> 00:20:46,610
Are you afraid of the thunder?

336
00:20:50,980 --> 00:20:52,180
It's personal.

337
00:20:53,370 --> 00:20:55,090
Let's not make it
part of the conversation.

338
00:20:55,980 --> 00:20:57,050
Jiang Li.

339
00:20:58,090 --> 00:20:58,810
Show some respect.

340
00:20:59,940 --> 00:21:01,530
The nights of Qingcheng Mountain

341
00:21:03,370 --> 00:21:04,900
are piercing cold.

342
00:21:06,020 --> 00:21:08,330
It's cold enough to open your eyes.

343
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:11,290
I never understood

344
00:21:12,370 --> 00:21:17,050
why my loved ones
would be so cold to me.

345
00:21:25,850 --> 00:21:30,090
They made me stay
on Qingcheng Mountain for ten years.

346
00:21:34,130 --> 00:21:35,810
But I get it now.

347
00:21:38,740 --> 00:21:40,610
I saw the money my mother left you.

348
00:21:42,130 --> 00:21:43,610
I know I misunderstood.

349
00:21:45,290 --> 00:21:47,610
My mother still cares about me.

350
00:21:48,460 --> 00:21:50,660
Therefore, I have a request.

351
00:21:51,660 --> 00:21:53,180
I survived ten years

352
00:21:54,980 --> 00:21:57,220
on Qingcheng Mountain.

353
00:21:57,810 --> 00:22:00,610
Now, I only want to rely on myself.

354
00:22:01,770 --> 00:22:03,530
I hope you are fair

355
00:22:04,570 --> 00:22:06,610
in your judgment.

356
00:22:27,340 --> 00:22:28,170
[The shaded peaks
of Zhongnan are beautiful.]

357
00:22:28,170 --> 00:22:29,060
[Snow accumulates,
floating at the cloud's edge.]

358
00:22:29,060 --> 00:22:30,120
[The forest's outline reveals
the vivid color after rain.]

359
00:22:30,120 --> 00:22:30,940
[In the city,
the evening cold intensifies.]

360
00:22:34,130 --> 00:22:35,260
The handwriting...

361
00:22:35,770 --> 00:22:36,740
Scholar Shen.

362
00:22:38,130 --> 00:22:38,980
What do you think?

363
00:22:40,770 --> 00:22:42,370
Will this earn me a spot?

364
00:22:46,020 --> 00:22:47,220
Based on my understanding,

365
00:22:48,700 --> 00:22:50,170
you are indeed talented.

366
00:22:52,370 --> 00:22:54,090
But you need a year or two

367
00:22:55,090 --> 00:22:56,540
before making it
into the School of Integrity.

368
00:22:57,130 --> 00:22:58,610
Since I have the talent,

369
00:22:59,460 --> 00:23:00,810
why the wait?

370
00:23:04,940 --> 00:23:06,260
Why won't you look at me?

371
00:23:11,540 --> 00:23:13,540
I will inform Prime Minister Jiang
of the result.

372
00:23:14,090 --> 00:23:15,090
It's getting late.

373
00:23:15,500 --> 00:23:16,170
I must go.

374
00:23:16,890 --> 00:23:18,540
Do you hate me?

375
00:23:19,300 --> 00:23:20,940
Or did I offend you in some way?

376
00:23:23,370 --> 00:23:24,570
Why would you ask?

377
00:23:24,890 --> 00:23:26,330
Why must you do this to me?

378
00:23:29,060 --> 00:23:30,650
Did you do this?

379
00:23:31,060 --> 00:23:32,780
Why must you do this to me?

380
00:23:37,810 --> 00:23:38,700
Why?

381
00:23:40,780 --> 00:23:41,370
You...

382
00:23:42,260 --> 00:23:46,700
The people claim
that you are ever so righteous

383
00:23:46,810 --> 00:23:47,980
and stand against the objections.

384
00:23:49,460 --> 00:23:52,020
You carved a new path
of Imperial Examination for the poor.

385
00:23:52,650 --> 00:23:53,850
You are righteous

386
00:23:54,370 --> 00:23:55,500
and virtuous.

387
00:23:56,940 --> 00:23:58,380
I only ask

388
00:23:58,380 --> 00:24:00,190
for a chance of education.

389
00:24:01,950 --> 00:24:04,030
You know I am just as good as others.

390
00:24:04,860 --> 00:24:06,470
I am worthy of being
in the School of Integrity.

391
00:24:07,670 --> 00:24:11,620
But you are thinking about
getting rid of me at this very moment.

392
00:24:12,470 --> 00:24:14,340
Was I wrong about you?

393
00:24:15,190 --> 00:24:17,140
Or were the people mistaken?

394
00:24:17,780 --> 00:24:20,060
Is your conscience clear?

395
00:24:34,100 --> 00:24:35,300
Is my conscience clear?

396
00:24:47,300 --> 00:24:50,190
[Learning virtues and knowledge]

397
00:24:50,220 --> 00:24:51,130
Scholar Shen.

398
00:24:52,620 --> 00:24:53,300
Well?

399
00:24:54,580 --> 00:24:56,300
Is Li worthy of the School of Integrity

400
00:24:56,620 --> 00:24:58,620
with her current capabilities?

401
00:25:00,100 --> 00:25:01,750
Despite the years
she spent on the mountain,

402
00:25:02,270 --> 00:25:03,540
she is knowledgeable.

403
00:25:03,990 --> 00:25:05,190
She is a prodigy

404
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:06,380
of great talents.

405
00:25:07,540 --> 00:25:09,580
But the School of Integrity
is meant for female scholars.

406
00:25:09,860 --> 00:25:10,820
I think

407
00:25:11,510 --> 00:25:13,380
she would fare better
if she were tutored

408
00:25:13,660 --> 00:25:14,860
for another year.

409
00:25:17,580 --> 00:25:18,950
In that case,

410
00:25:19,510 --> 00:25:21,510
we'll proceed with your suggestion.

411
00:25:22,820 --> 00:25:24,140
I take my leave now.

412
00:25:25,270 --> 00:25:25,820
Yes.

413
00:25:26,750 --> 00:25:27,820
I'll see you off.

414
00:25:33,420 --> 00:25:34,580
[Learning virtues and knowledge]

415
00:25:43,380 --> 00:25:45,420
Why are you reading
Ruyun's books for the entrance exam?

416
00:25:45,950 --> 00:25:47,380
This is too deep for Ruyun.

417
00:25:47,550 --> 00:25:49,030
If I study this, I can teach her.

418
00:25:51,580 --> 00:25:52,790
You want to be
in the School of Integrity?

419
00:25:57,750 --> 00:25:59,100
If I weren't married,

420
00:25:59,900 --> 00:26:01,580
I'd go to the school for sure.

421
00:26:06,300 --> 00:26:09,100
♪Our tears merge into a river♪

422
00:26:13,310 --> 00:26:14,180
Scholar Shen.

423
00:26:14,620 --> 00:26:15,310
Safe travel.

424
00:26:20,100 --> 00:26:21,710
There is a strength I admire

425
00:26:22,340 --> 00:26:23,580
about Jiang Li.

426
00:26:24,230 --> 00:26:25,550
Do tell.

427
00:26:27,710 --> 00:26:29,070
I came from an impoverished family.

428
00:26:29,550 --> 00:26:30,510
As an official,

429
00:26:30,950 --> 00:26:33,950
I've seen many who use education
as a front for personal gains.

430
00:26:33,950 --> 00:26:34,340
[Jiang's Residence]

431
00:26:34,340 --> 00:26:36,710
Jiang Li's desire to pursue knowledge

432
00:26:37,180 --> 00:26:38,230
is truly hard to come by.

433
00:26:38,990 --> 00:26:40,900
The bar to get into the school is high.

434
00:26:41,510 --> 00:26:44,180
But a year's delay
will undermine her determination.

435
00:26:44,860 --> 00:26:45,750
It's not worth it.

436
00:26:48,420 --> 00:26:52,140
♪So too does hatred linger♪

437
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:16,380
I heard it myself

438
00:27:16,900 --> 00:27:19,380
that it's better to send her
to the school next year.

439
00:27:19,900 --> 00:27:21,620
Why did he change his mind?

440
00:27:21,820 --> 00:27:24,470
Perhaps Scholar Shen mentioned
something to him

441
00:27:24,580 --> 00:27:25,820
when he saw him off.

442
00:27:26,230 --> 00:27:27,470
But now,

443
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:30,070
His Lordship got someone
to help Jiang Li pack her belongings.

444
00:27:32,750 --> 00:27:33,510
Mother!

445
00:27:34,100 --> 00:27:34,750
Mother!

446
00:27:35,230 --> 00:27:36,230
Have you heard?

447
00:27:36,470 --> 00:27:38,710
Jiang Li is leaving
for the School of Integrity.

448
00:27:39,710 --> 00:27:40,710
Get back to your practice.

449
00:27:41,510 --> 00:27:42,340
Mother!

450
00:27:42,660 --> 00:27:44,070
Why didn't you stop her?

451
00:27:44,380 --> 00:27:45,230
Do you expect me

452
00:27:45,380 --> 00:27:47,550
to be her sister in school?

453
00:27:47,710 --> 00:27:50,030
You dare raise your voice against me
over this trivial matter?

454
00:27:50,270 --> 00:27:52,620
Do you remember nothing
about my lesson on composure?

455
00:27:53,270 --> 00:27:55,030
Do you think your privileged background

456
00:27:55,030 --> 00:27:56,070
and music talent

457
00:27:56,620 --> 00:27:58,310
is not as good as that girl
from the mountain?

458
00:27:59,030 --> 00:27:59,340
But I...

459
00:27:59,340 --> 00:28:00,470
Go back to your practice.

460
00:28:17,710 --> 00:28:19,140
Any updates from the scouts?

461
00:28:19,710 --> 00:28:20,340
The shop is open.

462
00:28:20,340 --> 00:28:21,510
No news as of now.

463
00:28:22,100 --> 00:28:22,860
Watch closely.

464
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:24,100
If Yang Song is dead,

465
00:28:24,100 --> 00:28:26,070
we get no money
out of the Bureau of Salt and Iron.

466
00:28:26,710 --> 00:28:28,750
But the business
with Li Zhongnan goes on.

467
00:28:29,380 --> 00:28:30,660
One link will move the other.

468
00:28:31,180 --> 00:28:32,580
He will make a move.

469
00:28:33,030 --> 00:28:33,620
Yes.

470
00:28:34,230 --> 00:28:34,900
My Lord.

471
00:28:35,380 --> 00:28:38,070
It's said there are changes
to the Entry Exam this year.

472
00:28:39,340 --> 00:28:40,100
How so?

473
00:28:40,790 --> 00:28:42,140
Princess Wanning went to His Majesty

474
00:28:42,140 --> 00:28:44,070
and proposed that both schools
take the same exam.

475
00:28:44,140 --> 00:28:45,820
The students must sit
for the exam in teams.

476
00:28:46,180 --> 00:28:47,860
His Majesty approved.

477
00:28:49,180 --> 00:28:51,270
Is Shen Yurong still the examiner?

478
00:28:51,510 --> 00:28:52,030
Yes.

479
00:28:54,820 --> 00:28:56,580
The new system undoubtedly

480
00:28:56,580 --> 00:28:58,140
provides the rich and powerful

481
00:28:58,140 --> 00:29:00,340
a chance to openly partner up.

482
00:29:01,100 --> 00:29:02,230
Shen Yurong

483
00:29:02,230 --> 00:29:04,750
never openly fawned over
any rich or powerful families.

484
00:29:04,900 --> 00:29:06,580
He hates the forming of factions.

485
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:09,750
It seems

486
00:29:10,620 --> 00:29:12,660
things are more interesting
than expected.

487
00:29:13,030 --> 00:29:14,820
There's more.

488
00:29:15,230 --> 00:29:17,820
Shen Yurong helped Jiang Li
make it into the School of Integrity.

489
00:29:19,030 --> 00:29:21,030
Well played.

490
00:29:23,030 --> 00:29:23,820
I should keep watching.

491
00:29:27,700 --> 00:29:31,220
[Conceal the talent
and draw no attention]

492
00:29:37,710 --> 00:29:40,030
How could you be so cruel

493
00:29:40,340 --> 00:29:42,750
as to ruin my reputation?

494
00:29:43,860 --> 00:29:45,990
You'd even bury me alive!

495
00:29:46,710 --> 00:29:48,510
Have you been to Qingcheng Mountain?

496
00:29:49,100 --> 00:29:51,340
The nights are piercing cold.

497
00:29:52,550 --> 00:29:54,820
It's cold enough to open your eyes.

498
00:29:55,230 --> 00:29:57,030
I never understood

499
00:29:57,510 --> 00:29:59,340
why my loved ones
would be so cold to me.

500
00:29:59,550 --> 00:30:01,180
Scholar Shen, do you hate me?

501
00:30:01,550 --> 00:30:03,030
Why must you do this to me?

502
00:30:03,180 --> 00:30:03,950
Why?

503
00:30:12,380 --> 00:30:13,030
Yurong?

504
00:30:14,030 --> 00:30:15,140
The food is ready.

505
00:30:16,180 --> 00:30:16,820
Yurong?

506
00:30:17,420 --> 00:30:18,070
Yurong?

507
00:30:19,140 --> 00:30:19,790
Yurong?

508
00:30:20,990 --> 00:30:21,790
Answer me.

509
00:30:21,790 --> 00:30:23,140
Why are you locking yourself in there?

510
00:30:24,750 --> 00:30:26,100
Come out and have your food.

511
00:30:33,270 --> 00:30:34,310
There's a storm.

512
00:30:34,310 --> 00:30:35,470
Where are you going, Yurong?

513
00:31:36,780 --> 00:31:38,180
[Jiang's Residence.]

514
00:31:38,180 --> 00:31:39,550
As you expected,

515
00:31:39,950 --> 00:31:41,380
someone did go through

516
00:31:41,620 --> 00:31:42,860
the grave of the mistress.

517
00:31:43,340 --> 00:31:44,790
He has already been paranoid.

518
00:31:45,380 --> 00:31:47,100
We will be safe for some time.

519
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:50,180
You were right to expect it.

520
00:32:03,580 --> 00:32:04,750
Help her change into my clothing.

521
00:32:05,580 --> 00:32:07,310
She is gone.

522
00:32:07,510 --> 00:32:09,140
Why should she wear your ragged clothes?

523
00:32:10,180 --> 00:32:11,070
Do as I say.

524
00:32:13,380 --> 00:32:14,860
I'll explain everything one day.

525
00:32:18,790 --> 00:32:20,380
I feel sorry for Jiang Li.

526
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:23,550
Even in death, she couldn't have peace.

527
00:32:23,950 --> 00:32:24,710
Miss.

528
00:32:25,470 --> 00:32:27,990
Lady Jiang would watch over us.

529
00:32:28,750 --> 00:32:30,070
She wouldn't hold it against you.

530
00:32:33,660 --> 00:32:35,380
We cleared one obstacle.

531
00:32:37,990 --> 00:32:39,180
It's time.

532
00:32:39,900 --> 00:32:40,790
I must leave for school.

533
00:32:44,380 --> 00:32:44,990
Miss.

534
00:32:46,420 --> 00:32:47,790
Can I go with you?

535
00:32:48,510 --> 00:32:50,310
I'm worried for you.

536
00:32:51,620 --> 00:32:54,580
Do you know anyone
who brings their servant to school?

537
00:32:56,180 --> 00:32:56,860
But,

538
00:32:56,990 --> 00:32:58,230
ever since we left the Zhennv Hall

539
00:32:58,230 --> 00:32:59,510
and came back,

540
00:32:59,820 --> 00:33:01,180
I've never left your side.

541
00:33:01,510 --> 00:33:03,620
At least we'll have each other's back.

542
00:33:04,310 --> 00:33:06,180
If you're at school by yourself...

543
00:33:07,070 --> 00:33:07,990
I'm worried...

544
00:33:08,550 --> 00:33:10,180
Have you ever seen me get mistreated?

545
00:33:11,310 --> 00:33:12,140
You, on the other hand,

546
00:33:12,990 --> 00:33:14,230
must take good care of yourself

547
00:33:14,230 --> 00:33:15,710
while I'm away.

548
00:33:18,020 --> 00:33:25,580
[Jiang's Residence]

549
00:33:37,180 --> 00:33:39,750
The qin is broken. I got a new one.

550
00:33:43,270 --> 00:33:44,990
Perhaps we can sit closer.

551
00:33:48,310 --> 00:33:49,100
Never mind.

552
00:33:49,750 --> 00:33:51,100
You two may go on.

553
00:33:51,340 --> 00:33:52,820
I'll ask Mother for another carriage.

554
00:33:53,340 --> 00:33:55,270
It's a shame we can't go to school

555
00:33:55,420 --> 00:33:56,380
together.

556
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:59,140
See you at school.

557
00:34:00,270 --> 00:34:00,820
Sure.

558
00:34:05,100 --> 00:34:07,550
Miss, Ji left early today.

559
00:34:07,710 --> 00:34:09,140
Where can we get a carriage?

560
00:34:09,990 --> 00:34:10,550
Jiang Li.

561
00:34:14,070 --> 00:34:15,350
Aren't you going to school?

562
00:34:18,140 --> 00:34:18,950
Yes.

563
00:34:19,580 --> 00:34:20,580
I'm getting ready to leave.

564
00:34:21,220 --> 00:34:23,140
Where is your sisters' carriage?

565
