It couldn't be helped.

843
00:47:47,980 --> 00:47:50,060
Mr. Li insisted on taking the booth.

844
00:47:50,260 --> 00:47:51,460
I offered a different spot,

845
00:47:51,460 --> 00:47:53,100
but he wouldn't go.

846
00:47:54,140 --> 00:47:55,210
Mr. Li?

847
00:47:57,770 --> 00:47:58,770
We rarely get to meet.

848
00:47:59,460 --> 00:48:00,620
I'll sit by his table.

849
00:48:01,140 --> 00:48:03,260
Duke Su, they ordered us

850
00:48:03,430 --> 00:48:04,340
not to disturb them.

851
00:48:04,590 --> 00:48:05,300
So...

852
00:48:14,110 --> 00:48:15,340
Sons of the Li family.

853
00:48:16,180 --> 00:48:17,180
You're in a good mood today.

854
00:48:24,820 --> 00:48:27,180
What do you want, Duke Su?

855
00:48:27,700 --> 00:48:29,340
I'm not always working.

856
00:48:30,460 --> 00:48:32,980
Today, I'm here for some tea.

857
00:48:33,260 --> 00:48:34,700
The view here is stunning.

858
00:48:35,500 --> 00:48:38,250
But we've taken the spot.

859
00:48:38,900 --> 00:48:40,770
If it's tea you want,

860
00:48:40,940 --> 00:48:41,900
go somewhere else.

861
00:48:42,690 --> 00:48:44,060
As for the tea,

862
00:48:45,810 --> 00:48:46,620
the bill is on me.

863
00:48:47,170 --> 00:48:47,850
Never mind.

864
00:48:48,620 --> 00:48:51,460
I don't usually fancy a crowd.

865
00:48:52,170 --> 00:48:54,250
But I'm in a good mood today.

866
00:48:54,900 --> 00:48:55,850
I'll keep you company.

867
00:48:59,340 --> 00:49:01,940
Mr. Li, what say you?

868
00:49:35,200 --> 00:49:40,680
♪If there are no happy memories♪

869
00:49:42,800 --> 00:49:48,280
♪How can we traverse
the forbidden land of sorrow♪

870
00:49:50,080 --> 00:49:56,160
♪Two cold and unfeeling bodies♪

871
00:49:56,840 --> 00:50:04,120
♪Holding hands,
can we get through the snow season♪

872
00:50:05,160 --> 00:50:11,640
♪In the cold wind, in the long night♪

873
00:50:12,440 --> 00:50:18,720
♪Embracing the remaining warmth♪

874
00:50:20,000 --> 00:50:27,240
♪The depth of the sea, unfathomable♪

875
00:50:27,320 --> 00:50:33,320
♪Can it bury yesterday's sighs♪

876
00:50:34,000 --> 00:50:40,040
♪Continue to love,
cherishing it with my life♪

877
00:50:41,880 --> 00:50:48,600
♪Continue to live,
even with only a glimmer of hope♪

878
00:50:49,720 --> 00:50:56,520
♪Whether in sorrow or joy,
I believe in you♪

879
00:50:57,520 --> 00:51:03,440
♪I'd rather be trapped
in the world's extremes♪

880
00:51:04,160 --> 00:51:11,280
♪Continue to live,
exhausting all courage♪

881
00:51:11,520 --> 00:51:18,800
♪Continue to love,
until the breath runs out♪

882
00:51:19,680 --> 00:51:26,480
♪Traversing half a lifetime
of loneliness, just to meet you♪

883
00:51:27,080 --> 00:51:33,520
♪After the hardships,
never to part again♪

